Body: Description: Hi, we are doing an audit and see that there is inaccurate data shown under Device Control - Computers for some entries. An example of this is searching for the Serial number: HWT4T39WFJ . This populates with one of the entries with username “rhyscote”, although that one should be under a different Serial number. The CSV export shows the same information as what is in the UI with this example. Can you confirm why the information is showing inaccurately?
